<h2 class="govuk-heading-l">International Road Haulage Permits</h2>
<p class="govuk-body">From 1 February, you will need to use an ECMT permit to transit through EU countries to non-EU
    countries who are ECMT members, including Switzerland, or cross-trade between two EU countries.</p>
<p class="govuk-body">All other EU journeys will remain permit-free.</p>
